title: My Dog's Face contest Day 32: Lucy vs. Stella, Rosie vs. Fox
text:
It's Day 32 of The Oregonian/OregonLive's My Dog's Face contest. And you know what this means: It's the last day of the first round.
Voting starts at 10 a.m. and closes at 8:30 a.m. tomorrow morning, one vote per person. At 10 a.m. we'll announce yesterday's winner, and the first round will officially be finished.
So what's next? As much fun as this is, we're stepping up the pace a little. All Round 2 vote-offs will begin Oct. 6 (that's tomorrow), so don't forget to check back at oregonlive.com/pets to get your votes in. You'll have two days to vote for all your Small Dog choices, then two days to vote for your Large Dog picks.
Then we'll be down to our Sweet 16, Elite Eight and Final Four.
Yesterday's winners: Shaw and Bert
Today's matchups:
Small Dogs
Lucy, Pug mix (left) vs. Stella, a Border Collie-Black Lab-Chow Chow mix (right) Courtesy photos
